snippet.title: PSX Longplay [170] Nightmare Creatures 2
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Stenio Henrique

This is a survival horror game, reminds me a bit of Resident Evil, Silent Hill, Van Helsing, The House Of The Dead. The game features a song by Rob Zombie.
This is my first longplay PSX, enjoy -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
